Description: This effort conducts regular assessments of interoperability of Radio Control IED neutralization technologies in the
presence of battlefield and commercial radio frequency signals to ensure performance is maintained. This will be conducted with
foreign partners and hosted by different countries.

Title: Enhanced Personnel Borne IED Detection Prototyping                                                                              2.606            -         -
