identify, characterize deep space objects and report the results to Battle Management Command and Control locations and
the Space Surveillance Network. This major thrust was retitled from DARC Sites 2 and 3 Operational Capability to capture the
remaining scope of the DARC Site 1 prototype. The follow-on Major Capability Acquisition (MCA) will complete and field all three
DARC sites. It is not a New Start.

