Continue Site 2 design and development activities and complete Critical Design Review (CDR). Continue pre-construction
activities, to include environmental work and any requirements from UK Towne & Planning council. Prepare for connection of fiber
optics communication lines and infrastructure, such as the power grid, backup generators, and main water line. Begin purchasing
Site 2 long-lead and facility hardware.

