0609278A Project Code A87 Navigation Warfare and Budget Activity-5 (BA-5) Program Element (PE) 0604818A- Army Tactical
Command & Control Hardware & Software Project Codes EK6 Tactical Enhancement and EK9 Tactical Network Operations and
Management.
